---
title: Golden Crumbed Chicken & Gravy with Cheesy Potato Wedges & Creamy Avocado Slaw
description: A chicken schnitzel is a crowd pleaser, if you want to add a classic feel to the evening, drizzle over a rich gravy. It even goes well
with the easy cheesy wedges. Everything golden needs a bit of gravy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6528ffab9014a94c710fb9c9-c15fd2be.jpeg
